				\begin{document}$$w_i$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M36"><mml:msub><mml:mi>w</mml:mi><mml:mi>i</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13072_2020_346_Article_IEq14.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>), but imposing the weight reduces the score in example 3 below that of example 1 (Fig. <xref rid="Fig2" ref-type="fig">2</xref>c). We also demonstrate how the <inline-formula id="IEq15"><alternatives><tex-math id="M37">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
