    <p id="Par37">Regarding the performance of the SNP-independent scores (<bold>allelicmeth</bold>, deviations from 50% methylation and <inline-formula id="IEq102"><alternatives><tex-math id="M213">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
