				\begin{document}$$\text{ASM}_{\text{snp}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M218"><mml:msub><mml:mtext>ASM</mml:mtext><mml:mtext>snp</mml:mtext></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13072_2020_346_Article_IEq104.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>) and coverage increased, results were close to those of the <inline-formula id="IEq105"><alternatives><tex-math id="M219">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
