				\begin{document}$$\text{ASM}_{\text{snp}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M230"><mml:msub><mml:mtext>ASM</mml:mtext><mml:mtext>snp</mml:mtext></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13072_2020_346_Article_IEq110.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> scores are consistent in describing the CIMP status of samples, but as expected, the <inline-formula id="IEq111"><alternatives><tex-math id="M231">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
