				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\sim$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M238"><mml:mo>∼</mml:mo></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="13072_2020_346_Article_IEq114.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>40× more places in the genome where <inline-formula id="IEq115"><alternatives><tex-math id="M239">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
