    <sec id="Sec33">
      <title>DMR detection</title>
      <p id="Par67">We identified DMRs with the <bold>dmrseq</bold> R package (version 1.5.11) [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR47">47</xref>] for each cancer subtype. We specified the tissue via the <italic>testCovariate</italic> parameter (CIMP, non-CIMP or normal), and the patient with the <italic>adjustCovariate</italic> parameter. The <italic>cutoff</italic> parameter (cutoff of the single CpG coefficient that is used to discover candidate regions) was set as 0.05 and the rest of parameters were set as default.</p>
